  "merger_description": "Seismic Software, Inc (**Seismic**) proposes to acquire 100% of the share capital of Highspot, Inc. (**Highspot**), via merger.\n\nBoth Seismic and Highspot are US-headquartered business-to-business sales enablement software platforms which have Australian subsidiaries and customers. Sales enablement software platforms help improve enterprise sales teams\u2019 performance by providing document management and collaboration capabilities, data analytics capabilities and learning and coaching modules to build sales skills. Both parties\u2019 sales enablement platforms are enhanced by artificial intelligence. Both parties supply their products to customers across a range of industry sectors.\n\nSeismic is majority owned by Permira Advisers LLP (**Permira**). Permira would remain the controlling shareholder of Seismic following the proposed acquisition.",
